Gwamnatin Najeriya ta tabbatar da cewar yanzu haka mutane 32 ne suka mutu sannan wadansu 47 suka ji rauni sakamakon fashewar bam har sau biyu a garin Jos na jihar Filato dake arewacin kasar a yammacin ranar alhamis din ann.

Babban jami始i mai kula da hukumar bayar da agajin gaggawa NEMA Abdulsalam Mohammaed ya shaida ma manema labarai a ranar jumma始an nan cewa an riga an kai gawawwakin wadanda suka mutu dakin ajiye su a asibiti.

Abdulsalam Mohammed yace mutane 47 kuma da suka ji rauni suna karban jinya a asibitn kwararru na jami始ar Jos,asibitin kwararru na jami始ar Bingham da kuma asibitin our lady of apostle duka a cikin garin na Jos.
(Fatimah Jibril)

